Is this an automated out-of-office reply?

From: {from}
Subject: {subject}
Body: {body}

Look for:
- "Out of office" or "OOO" text
- Vacation/leave notifications
- Return dates
- Alternative contacts
- Automated response indicators
- Limited email access statements

Keywords: {keywords}

Is this a marketing or promotional email?

From: {from}
Subject: {subject}
Body: {body}

Look for:
- Promotional language (Sale!, Discount, Special Offer)
- Marketing campaigns
- Product announcements
- Sales pitches
- Promo codes or coupons
